376
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:34,580
 - It's the 13th floor! 
 - Who is that man?

377
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:07,020
Lei Wujie of the Lei family of Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect has come!

378
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:25,680
What are you doing?

379
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,640
There's nothing wrong, is there?

380
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:35,260

381
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:49,320
Nothing wrong?

382
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:53,420
How do you plan on compensating me?

383
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:55,200
Compensate you?

384
00:26:56,380 --> 00:26:58,220
Do you know what that is?

385
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:00,600
No.

386
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:05,660
Two deities were playing Go leisurely on Mount Tai.

387
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:08,320
It's said to be an endgame.

388
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:11,180
Hiding in the endgame is an exceptional martial arts skill.

389
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:16,820
If one person can comprehend the moves, it's better than 20 years of hard training.

390
00:27:16,820 --> 00:27:20,740
I was just about to figure it out when you walked in.

391
00:27:20,740 --> 00:27:23,380
So tell me, how are you going to compensate me?

392
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:29,840
Don't tell me it's another 500 silver taels.

393
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:33,500
What a good man! I'll give you a discount.

394
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:35,380
Three hundred silver taels will be enough.

395
00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:37,220
Three...

396
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:41,000
Then, can I pay you after I pass the trials?

397
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:42,800
Of course.

398
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:46,740
Great! Pardon me for this, then.

399
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:48,520
What do you want to bet?

400
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:54,680
Liubo, Pai Gow, Xuanhe, or Madiao.

401
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:57,620
I'm asking which you want to play. Pick one.

402
00:27:57,620 --> 00:27:59,860
I don't know any of these.

403
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:01,640
Not a single one?

404
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:03,420
Why did you come up here if you don't know?

405
00:28:03,420 --> 00:28:06,580
I... I only know one.

406
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:09,320
The big and small game.

407
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:13,100
Fine. Big and small, it is. How boring.

408
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:14,620
Come on.

409
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:20,900
We really can't compete in martial arts?

410
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:22,680
No.

411
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:30,200
One round to determine the winner. Take a guess.

412
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:34,060
Big!

413
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:42,920
Three, three, one. It's so small, it couldn't be smaller!

414
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,600
You lost.

415
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:51,020
It's my first time playing. So this round doesn't count.

416
00:28:51,020 --> 00:28:53,380
- Do you dare to have another round with me? 
 - Sure.

417
00:28:53,380 --> 00:28:54,860
I'll play another round with you.

418
00:28:54,860 --> 00:28:57,760
As long as you win one round, I'll consider you the winner. Come on.

419
00:28:57,760 --> 00:29:00,860
Wait! I'll go down the tower to have a bowl of soy milk first.

420
00:29:00,860 --> 00:29:02,900
I'll play the last round with you when I get back.

421
00:29:02,900 --> 00:29:04,640
Sure. Go ahead.

422
00:29:05,860 --> 00:29:08,820
- Don't forget to bring the silver taels you owe me! 
 - All right!

423
00:29:11,180 --> 00:29:13,440
What an interesting lad.

424
00:29:14,380 --> 00:29:17,140
 You're the one with the least advantage.

425
00:29:17,140 --> 00:29:21,560
 For some things, you have to try and fight for.

426
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:24,480
 If I don't try it, how will I know the outcome?

427
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:29,280
 If you fail, you'll die.

428
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:36,760
- Xiao Se. 
 - You lost on the 13th floor?

429
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:40,020
- You're weaker than I thought. 
 - I haven't lost yet!

430
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:41,820
That guy on the 13th floor doesn't want to compete in martial arts with me.

431
00:29:41,820 --> 00:29:44,460
He's playing dice with me.

432
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:46,800
You're a better gambler than me. Can you teach me?

433
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:50,080
I can teach you. But you need to pay more.

434
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:52,380
- How much? 
 - Another 300 silver taels.

435
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:55,580
- So it's a total of 800 silver taels. 
 - Eight...

436
00:29:55,580 --> 00:29:57,310
Fine!

437
00:29:58,020 --> 00:30:02,320
The person you met should be Yin Luoxia's disciple.

438
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:04,080
Yin Luoxia?

439
00:30:04,080 --> 00:30:06,760
Fairy Luoxia who split the Canglan River with one palm strike.

440
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:09,800
The one on the list of most beautiful women in the martial arts world for ten years?

441
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:12,420
- Are you still listening? 
 - Yes, of course.

442
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:18,140
Yin Luoxia loves gambling by nature.

443
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:21,860
She once lost three consecutive bets with Sikong Changfeng, the Spear Deity.

444
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:25,140
So she was forced to join Xueyue City as its elder.

445
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:27,540
It's said after she joined Xueyue City,

446
00:30:27,540 --> 00:30:32,700
she only accepted one disciple who loves gambling like her.

447
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:35,560
So tell me. What method did he use to gamble with you?

448
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:38,740
I can only make a random guess at first.

449
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:43,280
He... He opened it a crack and with one look said I lost.

450
00:30:44,120 --> 00:30:47,860
There's a hidden box under the treasure chest. He looked at the dice in advance.

451
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:52,040
If your guess was right, he'll only have to flick gently to roll the dice.

452
00:30:52,040 --> 00:30:54,360
You'll lose no matter what.

453
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:56,220
So that's what happened. I'm heading back now.

454
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:57,920
Come back here!

455
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:03,060
Gambling is nothing but a small trick.

456
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:05,240
Challenging Dengtian Tower isn't a trifling matter.

457
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:09,060
If you want to win, you still need to do what you're good at.

458
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:12,700
What am I good at?

459
00:31:12,700 --> 00:31:14,350
Beat him up.

460
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:16,590
I get it now.

461
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:18,220
He's out.

462
00:31:18,220 --> 00:31:20,200
- Excuse me! Make way! 
 - He only took a short break.

463
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:22,920
Not necessarily. There are 15 floors.

464
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:26,280
Martial Uncle, that man in red keeps running around.

465
00:31:26,280 --> 00:31:29,100
It looks like he was only taking a break and was not defeated.

466
00:31:29,100 --> 00:31:33,880
If this goes on, he'll steal away all of today's limelight!

467
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,380
There's no rush.

468
00:31:35,380 --> 00:31:40,260
When he reaches the 16th floor, watch me go up there and kick him out.

469
00:31:40,260 --> 00:31:44,040
It also saves us the energy of going up the floors one by one.

470
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:46,280
Since we're all waiting for him to come down,

471
00:31:46,300 --> 00:31:48,820
how about I invite you two to have some tea?

472
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:55,060
The crepe myrtle gazes at Qi, the all-seeing eyes seek the dragon.

473
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:57,400
What have you seen?

474
00:31:57,400 --> 00:32:00,140
Who are you? How did you know my martial uncle?

475
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:01,760
Feixuan, calm down.

476
00:32:01,760 --> 00:32:05,180
This man doesn't know martial arts.

477
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:07,980
There are three phases of Qi-Observing Arts.

478
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:10,920
You've only practiced the first phase.

479
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:14,720
Are you saying I misread your skills and that you're actually an expert?

480
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:17,120
No. You didn't misread me.

481
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:18,960
It's true I don't know martial arts.

482
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:22,120
I only want to invite you to have some tea.

483
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:24,840
Just for tea?

484
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:29,040
Since I've run into disciples of Mount Wangcheng, I will naturally want to ask you to do a reading.

485
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:32,020
You can stop hiding your identities.

486
00:32:32,020 --> 00:32:36,500
There's an organization in Xueyue City called Spiderweb that specializes in collecting intelligence.

487
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:41,380
From the moment we entered the southern part of this city, we were already being watched.

488
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:43,640
You seem to know a lot of things.

489
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:48,100
What I don't know is my fate.

490
00:32:48,100 --> 00:32:50,480
So I want to have it read.

491
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:52,160
Please come this way.

492
00:32:54,260 --> 00:32:57,840
Feixuan, didn't you always say you have mastered the Divination Arts,

493
00:32:57,840 --> 00:33:00,140
but you don't have someone talented to practice on?

494
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:02,460
There's one right there. Go and perform a divination for him.

495
00:33:03,180 --> 00:33:05,260
Talented subject?

496
00:33:05,260 --> 00:33:07,320
Just go. You don't have anything to lose.

497
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:08,680
Let's go.

498
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:14,640
You're back.

499
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:17,080
How was the soy milk?

