00:33:18,580 --> 00:33:22,120
After I reach the top of the tower, I'll treat you to a bowl.

501
00:33:23,220 --> 00:33:24,760
That confident?

502
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:30,580
My friend told me gambling actually relies on little tricks.

503
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:40,800
- So? 
 - So I'm still going to bet on big.

504
00:33:42,660 --> 00:33:44,320
We'll open if you're sure.

505
00:33:44,980 --> 00:33:48,000
If I want to win, I still need to use real skills.

506
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:49,700
Move your hand away!

507
00:33:58,540 --> 00:34:00,080
Six!

508
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,540
One!

509
00:34:19,740 --> 00:34:21,860
- Let go! 
 - No, you let go!

510
00:34:39,940 --> 00:34:41,280
- I said, let go! 
 - You let go!

511
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:43,460
If you don't let go, I'm going to bite you.

512
00:34:57,940 --> 00:35:00,460
One, one, six. So it's eight points.

513
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,780
No, it's 13 points!

514
00:35:03,780 --> 00:35:05,720
It's so big, couldn't be bigger!

515
00:35:10,420 --> 00:35:11,940
Not bad.

516
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:15,300
Your martial arts skills are a lot better than your gambling skills.

517
00:35:17,380 --> 00:35:20,280
I don't feel flattered at all.

518
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:23,160
What's your name?

519
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:26,900
Lei Wujie from the Jiangnan Thunderbolt Sect.

520
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:29,480
Didn't I tell you that before when I came up earlier?

521
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,860
I'm Luo Mingxuan.

522
00:35:32,620 --> 00:35:35,600
I know. You're Fairy Luoxia's disciple.

523
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:39,020
I've long admired Fairy Luoxia!

524
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:42,720
L-Long admired her?

525
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:45,120
What's wrong?

526
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:49,660
S-S-She's already over 30.

527
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:51,020
They said she split a river in half.

528
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:53,300
But the one she split isn't the Yangtze or Yellow River.

529
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:56,560
Why do you admire her?

530
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:57,500
Listen.

531
00:35:57,500 --> 00:36:00,440
She's actually an old woman.

532
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:03,320
 Mingxuan, come to Xizhao Pavilion.

533
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:06,200
I'd better get going to the upper floor.

534
00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:07,780
I'll see you around.

535
00:36:11,680 --> 00:36:13,700
What an interesting guy.

536
00:36:28,020 --> 00:36:29,700
I was only away from the city for half a day,

537
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:31,440
yet someone has already reached the 13th floor!

538
00:36:31,440 --> 00:36:33,260
What a bunch of useless garbage!

539
00:36:39,140 --> 00:36:41,000
Young Master, we can begin now.

540
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:41,800
Wait.

541
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:43,480
What now?

542
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:46,800
The person who's challenging the tower owes me 800 silver taels.

543
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:49,820
So I have to make an effort to support him in some way.

544
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,240
Xiao Se?

545
00:37:12,240 --> 00:37:15,240
Miss Sikong, it's been a while.

546
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:18,620
What took you so long to arrive?

547
00:37:18,620 --> 00:37:22,220
You were supposed to arrive at Xueyue City a month ago.

548
00:37:23,580 --> 00:37:25,640
I don't want to answer this question.

549
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:29,220
Martial Uncle, he passed the 13th floor!

550
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:31,280
He's heading to the 14th floor now!

551
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:37,620
Where's Lei Wujie?

552
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:41,800
Don't tell me... he's the one challenging the tower!

553
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:44,520
Miss Sikong, you guessed right.

554
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:47,660
We didn't have the time to spar last time because we bade farewell in a hurry.

555
00:37:47,660 --> 00:37:49,380
Now it's perfect.

556
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,200
