558
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:58,320
Are you trying to stop me on behalf of Lei Wujie?

559
00:38:03,100 --> 00:38:06,780
Martial Uncle, didn't you say that person doesn't know martial arts?

560
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,920
That's not a martial arts skill.

561
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,460
It's a lightness technique.

562
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:12,420
One doesn't need inner force to use it.

563
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:13,680
Which lightness technique?

564
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:17,360
The world's best lightness technique, Walking on Clouds.

565
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:27,140
