570
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:50,240
After all, we've gone through thick and thin together.

571
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:52,620
You're a Lei Clan disciple.

572
00:38:52,620 --> 00:38:56,340
If you want to join us, you only have to bring a visiting card and come see me.

573
00:38:56,340 --> 00:38:58,760
